	10 Principles / Characteristics of the Agile Tester.

	1.Provide continuous feedback to the team.

	2.Have courage.
	"Quality is the team responsibility"

	3.Keep it Simple.

	4.Self - organize.

	5.Face to Face communication.

	6.Deliver value/quality to the customer.

	7.Enjoy.

	8.Focus on people/team.

	9.Practice continuous improvement.

	10.Attend all important Scrum events.





